headline: Builders FirstSource Announces Definitive Agreement to Acquire Alpine Lumber
summary: DALLAS, December 23, 2024--Builders FirstSource, Inc. (NYSE: BLDR) ("Builders FirstSource" or the "Company") announced that it has entered into a definitive agreement to acquire Alpine Lumber Company ("Alpine").
